<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="11May1934"><font color="red">11 May 1934</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): Mr Morley &hellip; sent you and Mr Joyce a specimen page &hellip; the original page set up some years ago &hellip; anxious to know whether Mr Joyce still approved it. </div>
